    dc:title "The genus Paraplotes Laboissière, 1933 in Taiwan, a speciose group with brachelytrous females (Coleoptera: Chrysomelidae: Galerucinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235883>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235896>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235884>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235895> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235883>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 14. Diagnostic characters of Paraplotes cheni Lee, sp. nov. 9. Aedeagus, dorsal view; 10. Aedeagus, lateral view; 11. Aedeagus, ventral view; 12. Gonocoxae; 13. Ventrite VIII; 14. Spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/235883/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235896>
    dc:description "FIGURES 81 – 91. Hind wings. 81: male; 82 – 85: females. 81, Paraplotes taiwana, Tulanshan; 82, P. cheni, a & b, different individuals from same population; 83, P. j e ng i, a – c, different individuals from same population; 84, P. meihuai, a – c, different individuals from same population; 86, P. taiwana, a: Tulanshan, b: Motien, c: Tahanshan; 87, P. tatakaensis; 88, P. ts oui, a: Chihlanshan, b: Lalashan, c: Taipingshan; 89, P. tsuenensis, a & b, different individuals from same population; 90, P. y ao i, a: Machiatsun, b: Tengchih, c: Tona, d & e: Taoyuan; 91. P. yuae, a: Wushihken; b: Anmashan, c: Wuchihshan." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/235896/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235884>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 20. Diagnostic characters of Paraplotes jengi Lee, sp. nov. 15. Aedeagus, dorsal view; 16. Aedeagus, lateral view; 17. Aedeagus, ventral view; 18. Gonocoxae; 19. Ventrite VIII; 20. Spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/235884/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.235895>
    dc:description "FIGURES 79 – 80. Distribution map of Paraplotes species of Taiwan, solid line: 1000 m, broken line: 2000 m. 79. Widespread species, brown dots: P. tsoui, green dots: P. y ua e, pink dots: P. jengi, red dots: P. y a oi, blue dots: P. taiwana; 80. Localized species, brown dots: P. tahsiangi, pink dot: P. tsuenensis, green dots: P. tatakaensis, red dots: P. meihuai, blue dot: P. cheni." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/235895/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

